(10, 11, 'vi', 'Phương thức thanh toán cho mua hàng qua mạng', '<p>\r\n	T&ocirc;i c&oacute; thể sử dụng phương thức n&agrave;o để mua h&agrave;ng trực tiếp tr&ecirc;n trang web của c&ocirc;ng ty Hoalư? Hiện nay c&oacute; rất nhiều trang web cung cấp dịch vụ thanh to&aacute;n trực tuyến . C&ocirc;ng ty ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i đang nghi&ecirc;n cứu v&agrave; cập nhật chức năng n&agrave;y . V&igrave; vậy, hiện tại nếu bạn chọn lựa được một sản phẩm ưng &yacute; tr&ecirc;n trang web của ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i, xin vui l&ograve;ng thanh to&aacute;n theo c&aacute;c c&aacute;ch sau:<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; Chuyển khoản qua ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Thanh to&aacute;n tại cửa h&agrave;ngb&aacute;n lẻ của ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i<br />\r\n	Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i rất mong c&oacute; cơ hội được hợp t&aacute;c với bạn.<br />\r\n	Nếu bạn thấy c&acirc;u trả lời n&agrave;y chưa ph&ugrave; hợp, xin vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n hệ với ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i .<br />\r\n	Tr&acirc;n trọng cảm ơn.</p>\r\n', 1),
(11, 11, 'vi', 'Tôi có thể nhận được hàng mẫu không', '<p>\r\n	T&ocirc;i c&oacute; thể nhận được h&agrave;ng mẫu kh&ocirc;ng ? &nbsp;<br />\r\n	L&agrave;m thế n&agrave;o để c&oacute; thể nhận được h&agrave;ng mẫu của c&ocirc;ng ty ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ?<br />\r\n	C&ocirc;ng ty ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i chấp nhận gửi h&agrave;ng mẫu cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ở khắp mọi nơi tr&ecirc;n thế giới. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng thanh to&aacute;n cho ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i gi&aacute; của h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; v&agrave; gi&aacute; vận chuyển h&agrave;ng đến nơi m&agrave; bạn muốn. Nếu bạn muốn nhận h&agrave;ng mẫu, xin bạn vui l&ograve;ng thanh to&aacute;n cho ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ph&iacute; của h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; v&agrave; ph&iacute; vận chuyển h&agrave;ng .<br />\r\n	Sau khi nhận được h&agrave;ng mẫu, nếu:<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; bạn đặt h&agrave;ng v&agrave; gi&aacute; trị của đơn h&agrave;ng lớn hơn 500.00 USD<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;đơn gi&aacute; của h&agrave;ng mẫu nhỏ hơn 100.00 USD<br />\r\n	ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i sẽ ho&agrave;n trả ph&iacute; h&agrave;ng mẫu cho bạn.<br />\r\n	Bạn vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n hệ theo địa chỉ :<br />\r\n	C&ocirc;ng ty thủ c&ocirc;ng mỹ nghệ Hoa Lư<br />\r\n	Địa chỉ : 17-19 Đặng Dung, Ba Đ&igrave;nh, H&agrave; Nội<br />\r\n	Đt : 043 733 7364</p>\r\n', 1),
(12, 12, 'vi', 'HOW CAN I GET YOUR SAMPLE', '<p>\r\n	In case you would like to get one of our sample, which is available in our stock , please pay for the sample and the transport fee.The cost of the sample is retail price.Please pay in advance all deposit of sample. Before the order is placed, customers would always like us to send a sample. If the sample is in our stock, please pay the sample cost and the transport fee by air. If you are in a foreign country, please transfer money to our bank&#39;s account at&nbsp; Bank for foreign trade of Vietnam.<br />\r\n	Our all details for transfer money from aboard is :<br />\r\n	&nbsp;BANK FOR FOREIGN TRADE OF VIETNAM<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	Add : 198 Tran Quang Khai street, Hanoi, Vietnam<br />\r\n	Telex : 411504/411229 VCB -VT<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	Tel : +084 4 8251322,8240976<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	Swift : BFTV VNVX&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	TGMS : VIETCOMBANK<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	Account No. : 0011 3710 34816<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	Fax : 084 4 826 90673<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;<br />\r\n	As soon as we have received the deposit of the sample, we would send your sample by air.</p>\r\n', 1),
(13, 12, 'vi', 'How to know if the Distributor is real or not', '<p>\r\n	How to know if the Distributor is real or not ?<br />\r\n	&nbsp; Many customers worry about finding a real distributor.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;It is true, every business contains risks, to minimize the risks we need to have a strategy and information about the business it self, I just want to summarize and add a few point to this common problem.<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;You have to understand, doesn&#39;t matter the payment method is does not guarantee that it will make safe transaction.<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Information, you need to get as much as information before doing the transaction.Getting information from a forum also possible to get the feeling of trust before buying. A real distributor always publish their information on company&rsquo;s website, and other global B2B sites, for example: alibaba, EC21, globalsources,&hellip;<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;If they provide samples, then it would increase the feeling of safe transaction for you.<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Product Specification, if they can release this kind of document, that would give you more information about how proffesional the distributor is.<br />\r\n	&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Testing, yes you could test the validity of the distributor by buying something really really low prices just to get the response on how valid is the distributor.<br />\r\n	I hope I could help a little bit in here and yes ... buying something from oveseas is not easy not the same like buying in the superstore or traditional market. Once again ... you need to obtain more and more information before doing the transaction.</p>\r\n', 1),
(14, 12, 'vi', 'HOW TO SEE OUR PRODUCTS ON WEBSITE', '<p>\r\n	HOW TO SEE OUR PRODUCTS ON WEBSITE ?<br />\r\n	&nbsp;As you can see, our products are arranged in many different categories. Please click on any category, then you can see our range of products, all of which are made of the same material. Then, please click on the item you would like. There are many categories on the left of our website : &nbsp;<br />\r\n	1) Crocodile products<br />\r\n	2) Wooden ships<br />\r\n	3) Hoalu silk and fashion<br />\r\n	4) Embroidery items<br />\r\n	5) Traditional brocade<br />\r\n	6) Antique reproduction<br />\r\n	7) Bronze product<br />\r\n	......................<br />\r\n	In each category, there are many items .Please click on any image or name of the product, then you can see another window . On this window, you can see image, name, code, description and big image of the product. Should you want to know the price of the product, please send us an email or click on support online. We have two hot-line numbers: +084 977 901 014, and +084 988 715 009.<br />\r\n	We will reply you within 24 hours.<br />\r\n	Thank you and hope to cooperate with you in success.</p>\r\n', 1),
(15, 12, 'vi', 'HOW CAN I GET YOUR SAMPLE', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	In case you would like to get one of our sample, which is available in our stock , please ay for the sample and the transport fee.The cost of the sample is retail price.Please pay in advance all deposit of sample. Before the order is placed, customers would always like us to send a sample. If the sample is in our stock, please pay the sample cost and the transport fee by air. If you are in a foreign country, please transfer money to our bank&#39;s account at &nbsp;Bank for foreign trade of Vietnam.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Our all details for transfer money from aboard is :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;BANK FOR FOREIGN TRADE OF VIETNAM</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Add : 198 Tran Quang Khai street, Hanoi, Vietnam</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Telex : 411504/411229 VCB -VT</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Tel : +084 4 8251322,8240976&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Swift : BFTV VNVX</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	TGMS : VIETCOMBANK&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Account No. : 0011 3710 34816&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	As soon as we have received the deposit of the sample, we would send your sample by air.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 1);
